<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٨٠ - لِكُلِّ قَادِمٍ نَصِيبٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَا يُعْرَفُ بِهَذَا اللَّفْظِ لَكِنَّهُ فِي مَعْنَى<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣٨١ - الضَّيْفُ يَأْتِي بِرِزْقِهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣٨٢ - لِكُلِّ مُجْتَهِدٍ نَصِيبٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ وَهُوَ فِي مَعْنَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٣٨٣ - مَنْ طَلَبَ وَجَدَّ وَجَدَ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣٨٤ - لِكُلِّ مَقَامٍ مَقَالٌ وَلِكُلِّ زَمَانٍ رِجَالٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>جَاءَ عَنْ أَبِي الدَّرْدَاءِ وَأَبِي الطُّفَيْلِ مَوْقُوفًا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>